title: Sound Solution 1.31b (Winamp plugin, the one WITH all the preset
description:
This is Sound Solution, a Winamp plugin (works for latest Winamp version 5.666) which makes the sound much better. 

You have 90 presets to choose from, this plugin is hard to come by nowadays as the original website is down for a while already. 

I found this at a 4shared link with a lot of luck and decided to up it here to keep it alive!

Please keep seeding. File size is 100% correct and working.
